body:
Since i have alot of fucking spare time, ive decided to make a building group. We will make minecraft Maps, such as horror, adventure, parkour, ETC. Since im only a little kid, i;m not very experienced in the art of command  block use, or redstone. Altho, i am a fairly decent builder, and very creative and into writing. If you dont want to join, thats fine, i can make this post somewhere else.  and, Only post here if you have feedback, not some made-up shit to make me feel bad, i have feelings too.
Consider the following before applying
Redstone - Must be actually better than piston doors and such, and will work with people doing command block work
Builder - Must be known as good builder, or have screenshots of your beautiful work.
CommandBlock - Must know how to work easily with commands, and be ready to work with different sounds, particles, armor stands, and much more.
Creative mind - Must be actually creative, dont goof off, and be willing to cooperate with other people making the storyline
